cloudy; Charleston, S.C. 70 foggy; Chattanooga 71 rain; Cincinnati
63 cloudy; Cleveland 55 rain; Detroit 47 windy; Key West 82 partly
cloudy; Knoxville 68 foggy; Macon 71 partly cloudy; Miami 79 fair;
New York 64 partly cloudy; Philadelphia 67 partly cloudy;
Pittsburgh 66 showery; Portland, Maine 54 foggy; Richmond 67 partly
cloudy; Tampa 77 fair; Washington, D.C. 69 fair.
   _Central: Birmingham 72 foggy; Denver 31 snow; Des Moines 40
rain; Indianapolis 54 foggy; Kansas City 41 drizzle; Little Rock 66
partly cloudy; Louisville 65 rain; Memphis 71 foggy; Nashville 70
rain; New Orleans 74 cloudy; North Platte 35 cloudy; Oklahoma City
44 windy; Omaha 42 cloudy; Rapid City 25 partly cloudy; St. Louis
53 drizzle; Minneapolis-St. Paul 37 cloudy; Sault Ste. Marie 32
partly cloudy; San Antonio 71 fair.
   _West: Boise 38 fair; Casper 32 snow; Fairbanks 31 snow; Great
