foggy; Medford 43 fair; Pendleton 38 fair; Phoenix 72 fair;
Portland, Ore. 48 fair; Reno 48 fair; Salt Lake City 37 fair; San
Diego 62 foggy; San Francisco 54 fair; Seattle 52 cldy; Spokane 32
fair.
   _International: Calgary 28 fair; Montreal 45 cloudy; Ottawa 41
partly cloudy; Regina 21 fair; Toronto 43 drizzle; Winnipeg 32
foggy.
