<DATELINE>STAMFORD, Conn. (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   A man who accidentally smothered his baby
daughter, then fatally shot his wife four months later in an
argument over the infant's death has been sentenced to 20 years in
prison.
   Darryl Masheck, 25, of West Haven was sentenced Monday by Judge
Martin Nigro to the maximum term for first-degree manslaughter. He
pleaded guilty in the death of 22-year-old Pansy Masheck, whom he
