   Relatives said the baby's death led to the disintegration of the
couple's marriage, and Nigro noted that in the sentencing.
   ``If I were God, I would be able to change everything to the way
it was,'' he said. ``But I'm just here to enforce the law.''
   Masheck accidentally suffocated the couple's 2{-month-old
daughter, Shayla Nicole, on Oct. 12, 1988, as the two slept
together on a couch, according to police and a medical examiner.
