2.1007 Dutch guilders, up from 2.0805; 1372.00 Italian lire, down
from 1,372.50; 1.1740 Canadian dollars, down from 1.1765,
   The recommended gold price in London was fixed at $365.65 an
ounce this morning, down from $366.50 late Monday.
   In Zurich gold was quoted at $365.80 an ounce this morning, down
from $367 late Monday.
   Gold in Hong Kong dropped the equivalent of 42 cents an ounce
today, to close at $366.66.
   Silver bullion dropped one cent from late Monday's price in
London, trading at $5.10 an ounce.
